Text: New Personal Email Address for Bill Wagner Happy Holidays All I am just wanting to notify you all that I have a new personal email addressother than what you may have loaded in your address book Please begin to use this email address to communicate with me I did not get to send out HolidayChristmas cards this year to everyone so please accept this as my HolidaysChristmas and New Years Greetings May you all enjoy yourselves these next couple of weeks Best Wishes and Seasons Greetings Bill
